        [[fung1 so2 封鎖]],
        to seal up;
    - _(1)fung p(')(o\)(3)_
        [[fung1 pou3 封舖]]
        to shut up a shop;
    - _(1)fung (4)sh(u:)n_
        [[fung1 syun4 封船]],
        to taboo a boat for government use;
    - _yat(7) (1)fung sun(3)_
        [[jat1 fung1 seon3 一封信]]
        a letter;
    - _yat(7) (1)fung (4)ngan_
        [[jat1 fung1 ngan4 一封銀]],
